    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん、瑠依ちゃーん、瑠依ちゃーーーーん！\nあっ、いたー！！　瑠依ちゃーーーーーーん！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、さくら？　ど、どうしたの、そんなに慌てて？\n何か私に用事？　もしかして、急用とか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "急用も急用！　急用過ぎてマッハ3だよ！\n今日は瑠依ちゃんのお誕生日だよね！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "もうゼロコンマ一秒でも早くお祝いしたかったんだけど\nプレゼントがなかなか届かなくて！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.8666648865,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5433.3351135,
          "startTime": 49.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "でも！　さっき寮に届きました！　じゃーん！\nどうぞ、サニピと月ストのみんなで買ってみたんだ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.2,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4433.332586199996,
          "startTime": 55.6333325862
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "これ、今日発売の『ぷりてぃー★エンジェル』最新\nシリーズ、公式通販限定Blu-rayBOXじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.5032065271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "優に聞いたの？　これ、買おうか悩んでいたのよ\nまた舞台があるかもしれないし、観ておきたいなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ、喜んでくれて良かった～\nそれにしても、瑠依ちゃん達の舞台本当に凄かったよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "敵の幹部役のfranさんもキマってたし！\n「ケケケケッハラワタ引きずり出してやるケー！」って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか別の作品と混ざっていそうな気がするけれど\nそうね、ありがとう。舞台のお仕事、楽しかったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "あとあと！　瑠依ちゃん、ゲームにも出てたよね！\nサキュバスの役！　すっっっごくエッチだったよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "っ……そ、そう、ありがとう。そこまで、その……\nそういう内容ではなかったと思うけど、えぇ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.8666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことないよ！　キッスを迫るサキュバスの\n瑠依ちゃん、本当にドキドキで、エッチだったよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.8999954223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "私もいつか、サキュバスの役をやってみたいな～\n「あなたの枕元で、あずきを洗ってあげるわ」って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.8333297729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "あの、さくら……？　絶対、何か別の作品と混ざってる\n気がするんだけど……。妖怪みたいなこと言ってるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.1333206176,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "その、わ、私、そろそろお仕事だから行くわね？\nBlu-ray、今度みんなで観ましょうか。それじゃ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.0666386921,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4300.008138199984,
          "startTime": 157.3666468303
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 11900.008138199979,
          "startTime": 164.9666468303
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_02-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、うん！　お仕事頑張ってね～！\nすっごくエッチだったから自信持ってねー！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.8666305542,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4700.016276100001,
          "startTime": 165.5666468303
        }
      ]
    },
